so it was a way of her getting away from that

348
00:18:00,774 --> 00:18:03,570
她可以继续做她想做的事 在舞台上表演
and doing what she really wanted to do, which was stage.

349
00:18:26,835 --> 00:18:28,133
可以和我们讲讲
Can you talk about the play

350
00:18:29,337 --> 00:18:31,202
你们在蒙特利尔一起演出的那部剧么
that you were in together in Montreal?

351
00:18:31,339 --> 00:18:33,308
