He was writing about his experiences

361
00:18:52,629 --> 00:18:53,618
亲身经历
in the theater world.

362
00:18:53,764 --> 00:18:56,597
我扮演他新作品的导演
I played the director of his new play,

363
00:18:56,733 --> 00:18:59,702
韦恩・罗伯森和杰弗里・博斯
and Wayne Robson and Geoffrey Bowes

364
00:18:59,836 --> 00:19:01,930
扮演两位来试镜的演员
played actors who came in to audition.

365
00:19:02,073 --> 00:19:04,336
黛安扮演一位剧评人
And Diane played a reviewer.

366
00:19:04,474 --> 00:19:06,500
我对她说『黛安 你就像一个...』
I said, "Diane, you're like a kid

367
00:19:06,644 --> 00:19:09,942
『下课铃响就冲出教室的孩子 嘴里喊着“耶！”』
running out the door for recess,"going, "Yay!"

368
00:19:10,081 --> 00:19:11,070
她当时就是这样
And that's what she was like.

369
00:19:11,215 --> 00:19:14,412
