During the time that I was there,what was interesting,

376
00:19:26,699 --> 00:19:29,463
她不停地谈论迈克尔
I remember her talking about Michael a lot,

377
00:19:29,601 --> 00:19:32,900
因为迈克尔一直写情书给她
because Michael was writing her passionate letters.

378
00:19:33,038 --> 00:19:35,700
