But the thing about Diane is that

381
00:19:39,813 --> 00:19:42,873
当下发生了什么事
what was happening in her life at the moment

382
00:19:43,016 --> 00:19:44,347
她就会毫不避讳地与你谈论什么事
was what she talked about.

383
00:19:44,484 --> 00:19:47,977
她和你说话的时候 你可以感觉到她的毫无保留
As she talked,it felt like this was everything,

384
