But I realize now,it must have been a part.

387
00:19:55,962 --> 00:19:58,363
她确实是个藏着秘密的人
So what I'm saying is that she had secrets.

388
00:20:00,468 --> 00:20:04,302
排练进行到第二周时 迈克尔来探班
Michael visited her after the second rehearsal week

389
00:20:04,438 --> 00:20:06,031
发现她比前些年
and found her more alive and happy

390
00:20:06,174 --> 00:20:08,233
还要来得快乐
than she had been for many years.

391
00:20:09,578 --> 00:20:11,137
他和她共处了两个晚上
He stayed with her two nights,

392
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:12,576
