and they made love again

393
00:20:12,714 --> 00:20:15,616
倾泻着因短暂分离而赎回的激情
with all the passion that separation often brings.

394
00:20:16,384 --> 00:20:18,215
生活仿佛翻开了崭新的一页
Life was beginning again.

395
00:20:19,721 --> 00:20:22,588
你明白的 这些只不过是幻觉
You know all about it,and you know it's a delusion.

