重新和助手约翰尼一起
and went back full time into her casting business

403
00:20:55,327 --> 00:20:57,157
做起了选角导演的工作
with Johnny as her assistant.

404
00:20:57,930 --> 00:21:00,330
她和迈克尔的关系
Her relationship,on a sexual level at least,

405
