至少在性欲方面迎来了新的春天
with Michael was really blooming again,

406
00:21:03,701 --> 00:21:05,328
在分离一段时间之后
and after the long separation,

407
00:21:05,470 --> 00:21:07,496
他们仿佛变回了新婚夫妻
they were almost like newlyweds.

408
00:21:08,541 --> 00:21:11,340
几周后 她去看了医生
A few weeks later, she saw her doctor,

409
00:21:11,478 --> 00:21:13,469
得知自己怀孕的消息
who confirmed her pregnancy.

410
00:21:14,181 --> 00:21:15,705
她回家把这件事告诉迈克尔的时候
When she came home to tell Michael,

411
00:21:15,849 --> 00:21:17,577
心里相当不安
she was clearly upset.

412
00:21:17,716 --> 00:21:19,047
『我和医生谈过了』
"I've talked to the doctor,

413
00:21:19,185 --> 00:21:22,814
『他说我这个年龄再生孩子可能有点危险』
"and the doctor says it's a bit dangerous because of my age. "

414
00:21:22,955 --> 00:21:24,684
我说『那你打算怎么办』
I said,"So what are you going to do?"

415
00:21:24,824 --> 00:21:29,024
她说『我正考虑去做人工流产』
And she said, "I think I should seriously consider having an abortion. "

416
00:21:29,763 --> 00:21:32,631
我说『如果你想做掉的话』
I said, "If that's the way you feel about it,

417
00:21:33,701 --> 00:21:34,690
『我也不说什么』
"that's okay with me.

418
00:21:34,836 --> 00:21:35,767
『你做决定』
"This is your decision.

419
00:21:35,902 --> 00:21:37,301
『那是你的身体 不是我的』
"It's your body, not mine. "

420
00:21:37,437 --> 00:21:41,432
黛安说她觉得自己该把这孩子打掉
Diane said that she felt she should have the baby aborted,

421
00:21:41,577 --> 00:21:44,273
因为他们可能也养不起更多孩子了
as they could scarcely afford another.

422
