让她把孩子留下来
towards proceeding with the pregnancy.

437
00:22:23,953 --> 00:22:26,980
黛安本来都在医院预约好了人流手术
Diane did arrange to go to the hospital for an abortion,

438
00:22:27,759 --> 00:22:29,282
在往手术室走的时候
and we were actually on the way down

439
00:22:29,426 --> 00:22:30,917
她改变了主意
when she changed her mind.

440
00:22:31,062 --> 00:22:33,826
她突然说『我不能这样』
She suddenly said,"I can't go ahead with this. "

441
00:22:35,434 --> 00:22:36,695
很神奇 是不是
Amazing, isn't it?

442
00:22:36,835 --> 00:22:41,431
我是说 你差一点就不会出生在这个世界上了
I mean, how close we were to you never existing.

443
00:22:44,443 --> 00:22:47,310
但是这一点就足以让你反对人工流产了吧
It's almost enough to make you a anti-abortionist, isn't it?

444
00:22:51,017 --> 00:22:55,045
