她喜欢一切『新』的东西 你明白吧
She just loved new, you know?

446
00:22:58,089 --> 00:23:00,082
『新』是她的追求
New was what she was all about.

447
00:23:00,227 --> 00:23:02,127
如果 我说如果
If there's such a thing as,

448
00:23:02,262 --> 00:23:05,789
灵魂有老旧与年轻之别的话
in that spiritual sense,old souls and young souls,

449
00:23:05,933 --> 00:23:08,562
她的身体里一定居住着一个年轻的灵魂
she was a really young soul,I would say.

450
