It was a fine gesture,

463
00:23:43,038 --> 00:23:45,234
他们也很高兴能出演这部作品
and they were delighted to do the piece.

464
00:23:45,375 --> 00:23:48,708
《菲洛米娜》这部剧
Filumena was the play

