尽管我怀疑我们或许可以过到一起去
although I suspect that it would have been okay.

910
00:45:51,856 --> 00:45:53,484
我觉得我们应该可以
I know it would have been okay.

911
00:45:58,765 --> 00:46:00,858
我们两个人 我和哈利
Both of us, both Harry and I,

912
00:46:01,000 --> 00:46:03,468
都遇见了一个
met a person who was

913
