他们结了婚
They were married,

922
00:46:36,338 --> 00:46:40,501
我不清楚她对他感情有多深
and I don't know how deep her feelings were for him,

923
00:46:40,642 --> 00:46:41,940
但他对她用情很深
but his feelings were deep,

924
00:46:42,077 --> 00:46:44,443
这样的关系让人感觉不适
and it's awful to be in a relationship

