00:46:46,248 --> 00:46:48,740
远胜过对方爱自己
much more than the other person loves them,

927
00:46:48,885 --> 00:46:50,044
在所有的爱情关系里
and in every relationship,

928
00:46:50,186 --> 00:46:52,484
