but, hopefully, it's close,

930
00:46:54,724 --> 00:46:57,385
幸运的是 这种差距是会逐渐变化的
and, hopefully, it goes up and down a little bit,

931
00:46:58,195 --> 00:46:59,389
但在我看来
but it seems to me

932
00:46:59,529 --> 00:47:02,931
爱情里永远不存在平等的概念
you never can both equally love each other the same amount.

933
00:47:03,067 --> 00:47:05,933
这个不幸的事实恰好就是生活的真谛
It's unfortunate,but it's just a fact of life.

934
00:47:06,069 --> 00:47:09,597
乔治是妈妈的父母
George was the kind of guy that Mom's parents

935
00:47:09,740 --> 00:47:11,104
会很喜欢的那类人
would have been very happy with.

936
00:47:11,241 --> 00:47:14,507
因为他有钱有事业
He had money,and he had a good job.

937
00:47:14,645 --> 00:47:17,273
我一直觉得她太早嫁给他
So my sense has always been that she married him early,

938
00:47:17,415 --> 00:47:18,313
她嫁给他
and she married him

939
00:47:18,449 --> 00:47:21,112
只是因为他和她门当户对
because he was the kind of person she was supposed to marry.

940
00:47:21,253 --> 00:47:23,277
我觉得我爸对她管得多了一些
I think my dad was really controlling,

941
00:47:23,421 --> 00:47:26,016
而我妈一直很想摆脱这种束缚
and Mom wanted to get out from underneath that.

942
00:47:26,158 --> 00:47:28,889
